data.description: Don't miss out on one of the best lots in Bristol Trails, which is located on a cul-de-sac and overlooks tons of open space! Brand new architectural shingle roof! Kitchen with stainless steel dishwasher and refrigerator! First floor windows have been replaced! 6-panel doors throughout! White baseboards and trim! Located close to schools, parks, shopping, restaurants, and all Lake Zurich as to offer!
